  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nAs tested in #3448, throwing an object is 5x faster than our typed error (for example AttestationError), we should consider this option.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nconsider changing from\r\n```typescript\r\nthrow new AttestationError(GossipAction.IGNORE, {\r\n    code: AttestationErrorCode.UNKNOWN_BEACON_BLOCK_ROOT,\r\n    root: ZERO_HASH,\r\n  });\r\n```\r\n\r\nto\r\n```typescript\r\nthrow {\r\n    action: GossipAction.IGNORE,\r\n    code: AttestationErrorCode.UNKNOWN_BEACON_BLOCK_ROOT,\r\n    root: ZERO_HASH,\r\n  };\r\n```",
